overview: As Colonel Kadaffi hides in a bunker, he realizes his career is in shambles. An assistant recommends he find a Hollywood Agent to rebuild his career, so they take to the internet to discover WME. Kadaffi is so impressed, he decides he no longer wants to be their client, he wants to be an agent. Now WME must stop him as he insists on being "part of the team".
title: Kadaffi Goes Hollywood
